<code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION" />
<title>DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION</title>
<text><paragraph>Adults and children over 10: Usual dose is one 100 mg or 200 mg capsule t.i.d. as required. If necessary, up to 600 mg daily may be given.</paragraph></text>
<effectiveTime value="20081230" />
</section>
